Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,========================================  TEXT  ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来手续就都搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那么明天开学请多关照咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.56,0:00:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对我家彼方做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快停止你无谓的抵抗 马上放开你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not english
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没事啦 你说日语就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小遥 不是你想的那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到 布鲁玛高中排球部 沙滩排球支部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是彼方的沙排伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:03.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fax-0.2\blur2\fad(500,500)\bord0.2\pos(140.885,588.808)}想要取回从前的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以前玛莉莎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她们俩的母亲是我的教练 一起在打球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么自我介绍一遍 我叫托马斯·惠美理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这货是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,「这货」是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,双胞胎姐姐托马斯·红爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是两年级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我红爱就行了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,惠美理和红爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力泡芙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到了哦 之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们和成美的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 大家一起和以前一样打球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 红爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们俩能加入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就能更像一个像样的排球部了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入我加入 对吧彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那么事不宜迟马上练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能穿那种泳装啊 你是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这种泳装哪里不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,穿那种泳装我还不如穿内衣上场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就穿内衣打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说别人笨蛋的人才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,脱脱脱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,两位穿不同款式的不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 沙滩排球的衣服是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球是必须组队的人穿同样的泳装的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,无论对方是怎样的白痴都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,叫谁白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对姐姐还这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 彼方 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说要去练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么今天的项目是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想打比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,上来就？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,既然彼方这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,总之只来一场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我来发球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩有在好好听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比成美小姐还要快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 先拿一分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,明明很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再这样 我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再拿一分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,出界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,接球真粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,红爱 直线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要来了 直线球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看我拦网
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,红爱的球力道真强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才惠美理是用上手传球的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,惠美理的托球很标准 没有犯规
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果动作不正确 很容易被判为持球或者连击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,惠美理 直线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又是直线球 这次一定要拦下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,居然用这种手势击球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是吊球 改变扣球的动作来进攻对方的漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看来多亏了这身泳装 我现在感觉超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是 我对天发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 得一分就是一分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说她们两个从以前就是那样 不过是对好拍档呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,天真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方 别灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,直线球既然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我的扣球没法突破防线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,惠美理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又是吊球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你嘴上说这说那的 还是超有干劲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方 你为什么不吊球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,原本只打算练习 不过现在我改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要拦住彼方的扣球 明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好像碰到奇怪的开关了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,惠美理变成这样 我也拧不过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说吊球就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,又被那孩子的扣球锁定胜局了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真是强劲的力量选手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 真强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,下一场就是决赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不用扣球决胜 就不像我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像有点太爱管闲事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一次触球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,红爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,才不让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,遥的扣球也打得我很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,遥你力量也很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,被夸奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这对少女来说是好还是坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不是力量型选手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为个子矮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是用了吊球就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方 托球托球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然用吊球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 能进球就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 能拿一分是一分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能拿一分是一分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的我不是因为力量型选手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,才执着于扣球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为扣球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最容易得分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,进了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,勉强出界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的球越过拦网了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今天久违的打了一天比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到连续打会这么累
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小遥是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,连续打这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 两位都会加入沙滩排球支部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在加入的所有人 都能参加大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳沙滩排球 青少年锦标赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是官方比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,参加吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻决定？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,玩体育就是要比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧彼方 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 既然如此 开始特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教  魔鬼前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,魔鬼 什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉那两个人有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的事 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才想把自己的意见强加给彼方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,红爱说的对 我多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,惠美理这认真的一面 跟以往如出一辙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,反而有些放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看到刚才遥的吊球后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我回想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会毫不犹豫地选择吊球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 惠美理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找回那时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,找回 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,接球这个词 其实是从拉丁语里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,「再次」的re和「取得」的cipere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就是找回的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方一直都很擅长接球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以肯定没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,惠美理也顺便过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫顺便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个人完全没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次遇到她们是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟成美在青少年比赛的决赛上遇到了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,胜者 比嘉彼方 远井成美组合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,下一次 下一次一定赢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,以此为契机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也开始去玛莉莎那里练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小学的时候 是我邀请成美开始沙滩排球的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,成美是四年级的时候转校过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次见到她的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉她又高又成熟 特别帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很想跟她交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,正当我烦恼有没有契机的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球 要不要两人去试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉非常适合你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不行啊 还要穿泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,泳装不是很帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有句话不是说身体是运动员的武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 远井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要跟我一起打沙滩排球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,突然说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沙滩排球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那种我玩不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是远井你有身高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个一起的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,果然难度太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 刚才的事就当没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,跟比嘉同学你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,手这样握
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,既然练的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要不就以大会为目标吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大会？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是每天认真努力的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,每天练是不太可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么选我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你很帅啊 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也想跟你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是 多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们两个拼命练习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到了大会冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我就跟成美说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 我们真的拿了冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样全国第一也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既然彼方这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 说好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,之后你也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我逃离了成美还有沙排
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也没能完成约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在改变着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我一个人原地踏步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,变了的只有我一个而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但让我意识到这个的是小遥你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不过请我一起组队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,难得进了社团 也准备打比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一起正式组队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我这样的组队真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为打沙滩排球的彼方很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想跟彼方你一起打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:21:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这个明天不交的话会被红爱骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,彼方 你也快点写
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我已经写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候写的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,回来之后马上写的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这种要一起写的嘛
